El es mi hijo.

137
00:24:52,491 --> 00:24:54,254
- Señora...
- Hola Angus.

138
00:24:54,292 --> 00:24:55,520
Ross...

139
00:24:55,560 --> 00:24:57,152
Malcolm.

140
